---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Use Cases - Skief Labs" description="Real situations, real friction, real outcomes. See how Skief Labs builds data intelligence and sales acceleration systems for B2B teams.">
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-linen pt-20 pb-16 md:pt-28 md:pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <!-- Left: Text -->
        <div>
          <h1 class="page-hero-title heading-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[3.8rem] text-navy mb-8 leading-[1.1] uppercase">
            What this<br>looks like<br>in practice.
          </h1>
          <div class="page-hero-body text-black text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
            <p>This page shows the kinds of problems we're brought in to solve — and what the systems we build look like in real businesses. No demos or hypotheticals. If you recognize your business in any of these, it's usually a sign the underlying system needs attention.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Right: Document list graphic -->
        <div class="page-hero-image relative flex justify-center">
          <div class="w-full max-w-[420px] rounded-[10px] shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_#CFFF15] flex items-center justify-center p-8 md:p-10" style="background-color: #D9D9D9; aspect-ratio: 16/10;">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 355 145" class="w-full h-auto" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <defs>
                <linearGradient id="uc-sg" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
                  <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#0A60FF" stop-opacity="0"/>
                  <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#0A60FF" stop-opacity="0.22"/>
                </linearGradient>
                <filter id="uc-lf" x="-5%" y="-200%" width="110%" height="500%">
                  <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="2" result="b"/>
                  <feMerge><feMergeNode in="b"/><feMergeNode in="SourceGraphic"/></feMerge>
                </filter>
              </defs>

              <!-- Scanner beam -->
              <g id="uc-scan">
                <rect x="0" y="-20" width="355" height="20" fill="url(#uc-sg)"/>
                <line x1="0" y1="0" x2="355" y2="0" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-opacity="0.85" filter="url(#uc-lf)"/>
                <circle cx="89"  cy="0" r="2.2" fill="#0A60FF" fill-opacity="0.9"/>
                <circle cx="178" cy="0" r="2.2" fill="#0A60FF" fill-opacity="0.9"/>
                <circle cx="267" cy="0" r="2.2" fill="#0A60FF" fill-opacity="0.9"/>
              </g>

              <!-- 6 rows — y centers: 12, 36, 60, 84, 108, 133 -->
              <!-- Separators -->
              <line x1="0" y1="24"  x2="355" y2="24"  stroke="#555" stroke-width="0.8" stroke-opacity="0.18"/>
              <line x1="0" y1="48"  x2="355" y2="48"  stroke="#555" stroke-width="0.8" stroke-opacity="0.18"/>
              <line x1="0" y1="72"  x2="355" y2="72"  stroke="#555" stroke-width="0.8" stroke-opacity="0.18"/>
              <line x1="0" y1="96"  x2="355" y2="96"  stroke="#555" stroke-width="0.8" stroke-opacity="0.18"/>
              <line x1="0" y1="120" x2="355" y2="120" stroke="#555" stroke-width="0.8" stroke-opacity="0.18"/>

              <!-- Dots -->
              <circle id="uc-d1" cx="18" cy="12"  r="4" fill="#0A60FF"/>
              <circle id="uc-d2" cx="18" cy="36"  r="4" fill="#0A60FF"/>
              <circle id="uc-d3" cx="18" cy="60"  r="4" fill="#0A60FF"/>
              <circle id="uc-d4" cx="18" cy="84"  r="4" fill="#0A60FF"/>
              <circle id="uc-d5" cx="18" cy="108" r="4" fill="#0A60FF"/>
              <circle id="uc-d6" cx="18" cy="133" r="4" fill="#0A60FF"/>

              <!-- Row lines -->
              <line id="uc-r1t" x1="32" y1="8"   x2="308" y2="8"   stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-dasharray="276"/>
              <line id="uc-r1b" x1="32" y1="16"  x2="308" y2="16"  stroke="#001D52" stroke-width="1.1" stroke-dasharray="276"/>
              <line id="uc-r2t" x1="32" y1="32"  x2="308" y2="32"  stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-dasharray="276"/>
              <line id="uc-r2b" x1="32" y1="40"  x2="308" y2="40"  stroke="#001D52" stroke-width="1.1" stroke-dasharray="276"/>
              <line id="uc-r3t" x1="32" y1="56"  x2="308" y2="56"  stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-dasharray="276"/>
              <line id="uc-r3b" x1="32" y1="64"  x2="308" y2="64"  stroke="#001D52" stroke-width="1.1" stroke-dasharray="276"/>
              <line id="uc-r4t" x1="32" y1="80"  x2="308" y2="80"  stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-dasharray="276"/>
              <line id="uc-r4b" x1="32" y1="88"  x2="308" y2="88"  stroke="#001D52" stroke-width="1.1" stroke-dasharray="276"/>
              <line id="uc-r5t" x1="32" y1="104" x2="308" y2="104" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-dasharray="276"/>
              <line id="uc-r5b" x1="32" y1="112" x2="308" y2="112" stroke="#001D52" stroke-width="1.1" stroke-dasharray="276"/>
              <line id="uc-r6t" x1="32" y1="129" x2="308" y2="129" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-dasharray="276"/>
              <line id="uc-r6b" x1="32" y1="137" x2="308" y2="137" stroke="#001D52" stroke-width="1.1" stroke-dasharray="276"/>

              <!-- Pulse rings -->
              <circle id="uc-pr1" cx="18" cy="12"  r="4" fill="none" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.4"/>
              <circle id="uc-pr2" cx="18" cy="36"  r="4" fill="none" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.4"/>
              <circle id="uc-pr3" cx="18" cy="60"  r="4" fill="none" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.4"/>
              <circle id="uc-pr4" cx="18" cy="84"  r="4" fill="none" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.4"/>
              <circle id="uc-pr5" cx="18" cy="108" r="4" fill="none" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.4"/>
              <circle id="uc-pr6" cx="18" cy="133" r="4" fill="none" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <style>
            /*
              9s cycle. Scanner sweeps 4%→78% (rows hit at 13%, 27%, 42%, 57%, 72%).
              Lines oscillate (dashoffset yo-yo) until scanner reaches them, then settle:
                top  line → dashoffset 0   (full 276px)
                bottom line → dashoffset 90 (186px, shorter)
              Dot pulse rings expand on scanner hit. Dots glow after.
            */

            /* Scanner */
            @keyframes uc-scanner {
              0%, 3%  { transform: translateY(-2px);  opacity: 0;   }
              5%      { opacity: 0.7; }
              78%     { transform: translateY(138px); opacity: 0.7; }
              83%     { transform: translateY(138px); opacity: 0;   }
              100%    { transform: translateY(-2px);  opacity: 0;   }
            }
            #uc-scan { animation: uc-scanner 9s linear 1.3s infinite backwards; overflow: visible; }

            /* Row 1 — settles at 13% */
            @keyframes uc-r1t {
              0%  {stroke-dashoffset:180} 4%  {stroke-dashoffset:30}
              8%  {stroke-dashoffset:205} 11% {stroke-dashoffset:45}
              13% {stroke-dashoffset:0}   85% {stroke-dashoffset:0}
              89% {stroke-dashoffset:180} 100%{stroke-dashoffset:180}
            }
            @keyframes uc-r1b {
              0%  {stroke-dashoffset:145} 4%  {stroke-dashoffset:85}
              8%  {stroke-dashoffset:215} 11% {stroke-dashoffset:95}
              13% {stroke-dashoffset:90}  85% {stroke-dashoffset:90}
              89% {stroke-dashoffset:145} 100%{stroke-dashoffset:145}
            }
            #uc-r1t { animation: uc-r1t 9s linear 1.3s infinite backwards; }
            #uc-r1b { animation: uc-r1b 9s linear 1.3s infinite backwards; }

            /* Row 2 — settles at 27% */
            @keyframes uc-r2t {
              0%  {stroke-dashoffset:165} 4%  {stroke-dashoffset:35}
              8%  {stroke-dashoffset:200} 12% {stroke-dashoffset:50}
              16% {stroke-dashoffset:210} 20% {stroke-dashoffset:40}
              24% {stroke-dashoffset:185} 27% {stroke-dashoffset:0}
              85% {stroke-dashoffset:0}   89% {stroke-dashoffset:165}
              100%{stroke-dashoffset:165}
            }
            @keyframes uc-r2b {
              0%  {stroke-dashoffset:135} 4%  {stroke-dashoffset:70}
              8%  {stroke-dashoffset:220} 12% {stroke-dashoffset:85}
              16% {stroke-dashoffset:190} 20% {stroke-dashoffset:65}
              24% {stroke-dashoffset:205} 27% {stroke-dashoffset:90}
              85% {stroke-dashoffset:90}  89% {stroke-dashoffset:135}
              100%{stroke-dashoffset:135}
            }
            #uc-r2t { animation: uc-r2t 9s linear 1.3s infinite backwards; }
            #uc-r2b { animation: uc-r2b 9s linear 1.3s infinite backwards; }

            /* Row 3 — settles at 42% */
            @keyframes uc-r3t {
              0%  {stroke-dashoffset:175} 4%  {stroke-dashoffset:35}
              8%  {stroke-dashoffset:200} 12% {stroke-dashoffset:50}
              16% {stroke-dashoffset:205} 20% {stroke-dashoffset:30}
              24% {stroke-dashoffset:195} 28% {stroke-dashoffset:40}
              32% {stroke-dashoffset:210} 36% {stroke-dashoffset:25}
              40% {stroke-dashoffset:190} 42% {stroke-dashoffset:0}
              85% {stroke-dashoffset:0}   89% {stroke-dashoffset:175}
              100%{stroke-dashoffset:175}
            }
            @keyframes uc-r3b {
              0%  {stroke-dashoffset:155} 4%  {stroke-dashoffset:75}
              8%  {stroke-dashoffset:215} 12% {stroke-dashoffset:90}
              16% {stroke-dashoffset:195} 20% {stroke-dashoffset:60}
              24% {stroke-dashoffset:210} 28% {stroke-dashoffset:80}
              32% {stroke-dashoffset:200} 36% {stroke-dashoffset:65}
              40% {stroke-dashoffset:195} 42% {stroke-dashoffset:90}
              85% {stroke-dashoffset:90}  89% {stroke-dashoffset:155}
              100%{stroke-dashoffset:155}
            }
            #uc-r3t { animation: uc-r3t 9s linear 1.3s infinite backwards; }
            #uc-r3b { animation: uc-r3b 9s linear 1.3s infinite backwards; }

            /* Row 4 — settles at 57% */
            @keyframes uc-r4t {
              0%  {stroke-dashoffset:170} 4%  {stroke-dashoffset:30}
              8%  {stroke-dashoffset:200} 12% {stroke-dashoffset:55}
              16% {stroke-dashoffset:195} 20% {stroke-dashoffset:35}
              24% {stroke-dashoffset:210} 28% {stroke-dashoffset:50}
              32% {stroke-dashoffset:185} 36% {stroke-dashoffset:40}
              40% {stroke-dashoffset:205} 44% {stroke-dashoffset:45}
              48% {stroke-dashoffset:195} 52% {stroke-dashoffset:30}
              57% {stroke-dashoffset:0}   85% {stroke-dashoffset:0}
              89% {stroke-dashoffset:170} 100%{stroke-dashoffset:170}
            }
            @keyframes uc-r4b {
              0%  {stroke-dashoffset:145} 4%  {stroke-dashoffset:70}
              8%  {stroke-dashoffset:220} 12% {stroke-dashoffset:85}
              16% {stroke-dashoffset:185} 20% {stroke-dashoffset:65}
              24% {stroke-dashoffset:210} 28% {stroke-dashoffset:80}
              32% {stroke-dashoffset:195} 36% {stroke-dashoffset:75}
              40% {stroke-dashoffset:215} 44% {stroke-dashoffset:90}
              48% {stroke-dashoffset:185} 52% {stroke-dashoffset:70}
              57% {stroke-dashoffset:90}  85% {stroke-dashoffset:90}
              89% {stroke-dashoffset:145} 100%{stroke-dashoffset:145}
            }
            #uc-r4t { animation: uc-r4t 9s linear 1.3s infinite backwards; }
            #uc-r4b { animation: uc-r4b 9s linear 1.3s infinite backwards; }

            /* Row 5 — settles at 72% */
            @keyframes uc-r5t {
              0%  {stroke-dashoffset:180} 4%  {stroke-dashoffset:35}
              8%  {stroke-dashoffset:205} 12% {stroke-dashoffset:50}
              16% {stroke-dashoffset:195} 20% {stroke-dashoffset:40}
              24% {stroke-dashoffset:215} 28% {stroke-dashoffset:45}
              32% {stroke-dashoffset:190} 36% {stroke-dashoffset:30}
              40% {stroke-dashoffset:200} 44% {stroke-dashoffset:55}
              48% {stroke-dashoffset:185} 52% {stroke-dashoffset:35}
              56% {stroke-dashoffset:210} 60% {stroke-dashoffset:50}
              64% {stroke-dashoffset:195} 68% {stroke-dashoffset:40}
              72% {stroke-dashoffset:0}   85% {stroke-dashoffset:0}
              89% {stroke-dashoffset:180} 100%{stroke-dashoffset:180}
            }
            @keyframes uc-r5b {
              0%  {stroke-dashoffset:150} 4%  {stroke-dashoffset:75}
              8%  {stroke-dashoffset:220} 12% {stroke-dashoffset:90}
              16% {stroke-dashoffset:190} 20% {stroke-dashoffset:70}
              24% {stroke-dashoffset:210} 28% {stroke-dashoffset:85}
              32% {stroke-dashoffset:195} 36% {stroke-dashoffset:65}
              40% {stroke-dashoffset:215} 44% {stroke-dashoffset:80}
              48% {stroke-dashoffset:190} 52% {stroke-dashoffset:75}
              56% {stroke-dashoffset:210} 60% {stroke-dashoffset:85}
              64% {stroke-dashoffset:195} 68% {stroke-dashoffset:70}
              72% {stroke-dashoffset:90}  85% {stroke-dashoffset:90}
              89% {stroke-dashoffset:150} 100%{stroke-dashoffset:150}
            }
            #uc-r5t { animation: uc-r5t 9s linear 1.3s infinite backwards; }
            #uc-r5b { animation: uc-r5b 9s linear 1.3s infinite backwards; }

            /* Row 6 — settles at 75% */
            @keyframes uc-r6t {
              0%  {stroke-dashoffset:175} 4%  {stroke-dashoffset:35}
              8%  {stroke-dashoffset:205} 12% {stroke-dashoffset:50}
              16% {stroke-dashoffset:195} 20% {stroke-dashoffset:40}
              24% {stroke-dashoffset:215} 28% {stroke-dashoffset:45}
              32% {stroke-dashoffset:190} 36% {stroke-dashoffset:30}
              40% {stroke-dashoffset:200} 44% {stroke-dashoffset:55}
              48% {stroke-dashoffset:185} 52% {stroke-dashoffset:35}
              56% {stroke-dashoffset:210} 60% {stroke-dashoffset:50}
              64% {stroke-dashoffset:195} 68% {stroke-dashoffset:40}
              72% {stroke-dashoffset:205} 75% {stroke-dashoffset:0}
              85% {stroke-dashoffset:0}   89% {stroke-dashoffset:175}
              100%{stroke-dashoffset:175}
            }
            @keyframes uc-r6b {
              0%  {stroke-dashoffset:150} 4%  {stroke-dashoffset:75}
              8%  {stroke-dashoffset:220} 12% {stroke-dashoffset:90}
              16% {stroke-dashoffset:190} 20% {stroke-dashoffset:70}
              24% {stroke-dashoffset:210} 28% {stroke-dashoffset:85}
              32% {stroke-dashoffset:195} 36% {stroke-dashoffset:65}
              40% {stroke-dashoffset:215} 44% {stroke-dashoffset:80}
              48% {stroke-dashoffset:190} 52% {stroke-dashoffset:75}
              56% {stroke-dashoffset:210} 60% {stroke-dashoffset:85}
              64% {stroke-dashoffset:195} 68% {stroke-dashoffset:70}
              72% {stroke-dashoffset:210} 75% {stroke-dashoffset:90}
              85% {stroke-dashoffset:90}  89% {stroke-dashoffset:150}
              100%{stroke-dashoffset:150}
            }
            #uc-r6t { animation: uc-r6t 9s linear 1.3s infinite backwards; }
            #uc-r6b { animation: uc-r6b 9s linear 1.3s infinite backwards; }

            /* Dot pulse rings */
            #uc-pr1,#uc-pr2,#uc-pr3,#uc-pr4,#uc-pr5,#uc-pr6 {
              transform-box: fill-box; transform-origin: center; opacity: 0;
            }
            @keyframes uc-pr1 {
              0%,11%{transform:scale(1);opacity:0} 13%{transform:scale(1);opacity:0.85}
              21%{transform:scale(2.8);opacity:0}  100%{opacity:0}
            }
            @keyframes uc-pr2 {
              0%,25%{transform:scale(1);opacity:0} 27%{transform:scale(1);opacity:0.85}
              35%{transform:scale(2.8);opacity:0}  100%{opacity:0}
            }
            @keyframes uc-pr3 {
              0%,40%{transform:scale(1);opacity:0} 42%{transform:scale(1);opacity:0.85}
              50%{transform:scale(2.8);opacity:0}  100%{opacity:0}
            }
            @keyframes uc-pr4 {
              0%,55%{transform:scale(1);opacity:0} 57%{transform:scale(1);opacity:0.85}
              65%{transform:scale(2.8);opacity:0}  100%{opacity:0}
            }
            @keyframes uc-pr5 {
              0%,70%{transform:scale(1);opacity:0} 72%{transform:scale(1);opacity:0.85}
              80%{transform:scale(2.8);opacity:0}  100%{opacity:0}
            }
            @keyframes uc-pr6 {
              0%,73%{transform:scale(1);opacity:0} 75%{transform:scale(1);opacity:0.85}
              83%{transform:scale(2.8);opacity:0}  100%{opacity:0}
            }
            #uc-pr1 { animation: uc-pr1 9s ease-out 1.3s infinite backwards; }
            #uc-pr2 { animation: uc-pr2 9s ease-out 1.3s infinite backwards; }
            #uc-pr3 { animation: uc-pr3 9s ease-out 1.3s infinite backwards; }
            #uc-pr4 { animation: uc-pr4 9s ease-out 1.3s infinite backwards; }
            #uc-pr5 { animation: uc-pr5 9s ease-out 1.3s infinite backwards; }
            #uc-pr6 { animation: uc-pr6 9s ease-out 1.3s infinite backwards; }

            /* Dot glow — persists after scanner passes until reset */
            @keyframes uc-d1g {
              0%,12%{filter:none} 14%,86%{filter:drop-shadow(0 0 4px #0A60FF)} 89%{filter:none} 100%{filter:none}
            }
            @keyframes uc-d2g {
              0%,26%{filter:none} 28%,86%{filter:drop-shadow(0 0 4px #0A60FF)} 89%{filter:none} 100%{filter:none}
            }
            @keyframes uc-d3g {
              0%,41%{filter:none} 43%,86%{filter:drop-shadow(0 0 4px #0A60FF)} 89%{filter:none} 100%{filter:none}
            }
            @keyframes uc-d4g {
              0%,56%{filter:none} 58%,86%{filter:drop-shadow(0 0 4px #0A60FF)} 89%{filter:none} 100%{filter:none}
            }
            @keyframes uc-d5g {
              0%,71%{filter:none} 73%,86%{filter:drop-shadow(0 0 4px #0A60FF)} 89%{filter:none} 100%{filter:none}
            }
            @keyframes uc-d6g {
              0%,74%{filter:none} 76%,86%{filter:drop-shadow(0 0 4px #0A60FF)} 89%{filter:none} 100%{filter:none}
            }
            #uc-d1 { animation: uc-d1g 9s linear 1.3s infinite backwards; }
            #uc-d2 { animation: uc-d2g 9s linear 1.3s infinite backwards; }
            #uc-d3 { animation: uc-d3g 9s linear 1.3s infinite backwards; }
            #uc-d4 { animation: uc-d4g 9s linear 1.3s infinite backwards; }
            #uc-d5 { animation: uc-d5g 9s linear 1.3s infinite backwards; }
            #uc-d6 { animation: uc-d6g 9s linear 1.3s infinite backwards; }
          </style>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DATA INTELLIGENCE USE CASES -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="page-hero-next font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-[2.2rem] text-navy mb-12 leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.02em]">Data Intelligence Use Cases</h2>

      <!-- Use Case 1 -->
      <div class="page-hero-next border-l-4 rounded-l-[10px] pl-8 pt-6 pb-8 mb-16" style="border-color: #001D52;">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[2fr_3fr] gap-8 lg:gap-16">
          <div>
            <p class="subhead-condensed text-xs tracking-[0.2em] mb-3 text-black">USE CASE 1</p>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl leading-[1.3] tracking-[-0.02em] text-black">Marketing team spending senior time on research that should be automated</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="black" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 8v5" stroke-linecap="round"/><circle cx="12" cy="16.5" r="1" fill="black" stroke="none"/></svg>
                <p class="subhead-condensed text-xs tracking-[0.15em] text-black">The Situation</p>
              </div>
              <p class="text-black text-sm leading-relaxed">A marketing team of four is running account-based campaigns. Before any campaign goes live, someone — usually a senior person — spends hours building and cleaning the target list. By the time the list is ready, some of it is already out of date.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="black" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
                <p class="subhead-condensed text-xs tracking-[0.15em] text-black">What We Built</p>
              </div>
              <p class="text-black text-sm leading-relaxed">A continuous data pipeline that sources, enriches, and qualifies target accounts automatically — filtered by ICP criteria the team defined once, updated on an ongoing basis. Campaign prep that used to take two days now takes thirty minutes.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-[10px] p-5" style="background-color: #D9D9D9;">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="#0A60FF" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7 17 17 7M7 7h10v10" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
                <p class="subhead-condensed text-xs tracking-[0.15em]" style="color: #0A60FF;">The Outcome</p>
              </div>
              <p class="text-black text-sm leading-relaxed">Senior time redirected to strategy and execution. Data quality improved. Campaign velocity increased. The research backlog eliminated.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Use Case 2 -->
      <div class="border-l-4 rounded-l-[10px] pl-8 pt-6 pb-8 mb-16 reveal" style="border-color: #001D52;">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[2fr_3fr] gap-8 lg:gap-16">
          <div>
            <p class="subhead-condensed text-xs tracking-[0.2em] mb-3 text-black">USE CASE 2</p>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl leading-[1.3] tracking-[-0.02em] text-black">HR team mapping a talent market manually every quarter</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="black" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 8v5" stroke-linecap="round"/><circle cx="12" cy="16.5" r="1" fill="black" stroke="none"/></svg>
